### Stock Trading Simulator API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### 1. Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com", 
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### 2. Login with demo user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "password": "demo123"
}

### 3. Get stock quote (no auth required)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stocks/AAPL/quote

### 4. Get all stocks (no auth required)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stocks

### 5. Get popular stocks (no auth required)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stocks/popular

### 6. Get user profile (requires auth - replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 7. Get portfolio (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/portfolio
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 8. Execute buy order (requires auth)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/trades/buy
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stockSymbol": "AAPL",
  "quantity": 5,
  "price": 189.50
}

### 9. Get trade history (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trades/history
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 10. Get portfolio summary (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/portfolio/summary
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
